message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product to you for $130. I believe it offers a great value at this price.
Hello Alice, thank you for your offer. I appreciate the value you're providing. I would like to counter with an offer of $100 for the product.
Thanks for your offer, Bob. I'm willing to come down a bit, how about $115?
Hi Alice, I appreciate your willingness to negotiate. Based on my budget, I can offer $110 for the product.
